$ Excel: Page Setup -> Page Layout -> Breaks

→ Microsoft/Office/Excel/GUI/Ribbon/tabs/Page-Layout/Page-Setup[*Page Layout* -> *Page Setup*] -> *Breaks*  allows to
  • Insert page breaks,
  • Remove page breaks and
  • Reset all page breaks

{ Managing page breaks in VBA

  In → development/languages/VBA[Visual Basic for Applications], page breaks can be managed like so:
code {
activeSheet.hPageBreaks.add before := cells(5,3)
activeSheet.vPageBreaks.add before := cells(5,3)

activeSheet.hPageBreaks(1).delete
activeSheet.vPageBreaks(1).delete

activeSheet.resetAllPageBreaks
code }

}

